1
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:45,130
[My Heroic Husband]

2
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:47,930
[Episode 35]

3
00:01:47,930 --> 00:01:54,010
[Badao Camps plans to save Fang Tian Lei]

4
00:02:20,669 --> 00:02:23,408
My dear, I'm done packing.

5
00:02:23,408 --> 00:02:26,269
Is there anything else you want to bring with you?

6
00:02:26,269 --> 00:02:28,170
You decide.

7
00:02:34,369 --> 00:02:36,489
You seem distracted.

8
00:02:39,949 --> 00:02:42,409
I'm afraid you need to go there alone tomorrow.

9
00:02:42,969 --> 00:02:45,509
I still have something to deal with.

10
00:02:48,409 --> 00:02:49,750
Okay.

11
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:54,009
I'll wait for you in Wudu. Take care of yourself.

12
00:02:56,370 --> 00:03:02,390
[Suburb of Wudu]

13
00:03:03,349 --> 00:03:04,849
Stop.

14
00:03:05,389 --> 00:03:08,109
It's hot today. Give him some water.

15
00:03:08,109 --> 00:03:11,789
Don't let him die on the way to Wudu!

16
00:03:20,369 --> 00:03:21,869
General Wang!

17
00:03:21,869 --> 00:03:24,409
Commander Ning? Why are you here?

18
00:03:24,409 --> 00:03:26,730
You can't go any further!

19
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:36,460
[Hanlin Mountain]

20
00:03:48,650 --> 00:03:52,429
It's already dark. Why haven't they arrived yet?

21
00:03:55,969 --> 00:03:57,788
Your Ladyship! Bad news! Your Ladyship!

22
00:03:57,788 --> 00:04:00,010
Wang Yan's army suddenly changed their route!

23
00:04:00,010 --> 00:04:02,409
They bypassed Hanlin Mountain and are going straight to Wudu right now!

24
00:04:02,409 --> 00:04:04,229
Impossible.

25
00:04:04,229 --> 00:04:07,048
Hanlin Mountain should be the quickest way. Why would they take a detour?

26
00:04:07,048 --> 00:04:08,988
It's because of Ning…

27
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:11,290
It's Army Advisor Ning.

28
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:12,408
Ning Yi?

29
00:04:12,408 --> 00:04:16,729
He rushed to tell Wang Yan to go another way and bypass Hanlin Mountain.

30
00:04:18,829 --> 00:04:21,149
Let's get ready.

31
00:04:21,149 --> 00:04:23,969
We're going... to Wudu!

32
00:04:23,969 --> 00:04:26,088
- Yes!
- Yes!

33
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:37,180
[Wudu]

34
00:04:49,650 --> 00:04:53,290
[Wudu]

35
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:55,560
[Wu]

36
00:05:05,670 --> 00:05:07,830
Greetings to Right Chancellor Qin!

37
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:10,889
General Wang, it must have been a tiring journey!

38
00:05:10,889 --> 00:05:14,410
Mo Ying, take Fang Tia Lei to the Secret Investigation Department.

39
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:15,930
Yes!

40
00:05:39,509 --> 00:05:43,409
Officer Liu, Right Chancellor Qin wants to find out the mastermind behind all this.

41
00:05:43,409 --> 00:05:46,369
I will try my best to find out!

42
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:03,109
Please forgive me! Please forgive me!

43
00:06:04,289 --> 00:06:07,249
Don't you have a thicker one?

44
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:35,610
I don't want this dagger anymore! Keep it to yourself!

45
00:06:35,610 --> 00:06:37,749
It almost got me killed!

46
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:43,229
It belongs to me after all.

47
00:06:43,229 --> 00:06:46,870
It's normal that you don't think it's handy.

48
00:06:53,829 --> 00:06:55,889
This one is for you.

49
00:06:55,889 --> 00:06:58,928
Try it. See if it's handy.

50
00:06:58,928 --> 00:07:01,309
You made the biggest contribution toward suppressing the rebellion in Lin'an.

51
00:07:01,309 --> 00:07:05,850
This is a reward that you deserve.

52
00:07:15,029 --> 00:07:18,910
This dagger is exquisitely made.

53
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:23,149
And it feels much lighter. It is better than that one indeed.

54
00:07:23,149 --> 00:07:28,889
But if I accepted this dagger, I'd still have to work for you!

55
00:07:28,889 --> 00:07:33,269
Not for me, but the Secret Investigation Department!

56
00:07:33,269 --> 00:07:35,649
There you go again! It's always the Secret Investigation Department!

57
00:07:35,649 --> 00:07:37,969
What on earth is it used for?

58
00:07:37,969 --> 00:07:41,149
The Secret Investigation Department was established by the late Emperor.

59
00:07:41,149 --> 00:07:45,728
Apart from carrying out secret investigations, the most important mission for us

60
00:07:45,728 --> 00:07:49,028
is to take back the six provinces near Qingyun that were invaded and occupied by Liang,

61
00:07:49,028 --> 00:07:51,609
and to protect our Wu Dynasty!

62
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:56,408
To take back the six provinces near Qingyun?

63
00:07:56,408 --> 00:07:59,509
What? You don't agree?

64
00:07:59,509 --> 00:08:01,149
That's not what I mean.

65
00:08:01,149 --> 00:08:03,970
It's also necessary to recover our lost territory.

66
00:08:03,970 --> 00:08:08,790
But we don't have to resort to force.

67
00:08:10,929 --> 00:08:15,449
Looks like you've changed a lot

68
00:08:15,969 --> 00:08:18,389
after the battle in Lin'an.

69
00:08:18,389 --> 00:08:20,329
Right Chancellor Qin,

70
00:08:20,329 --> 00:08:24,270
anyone would show compassion toward the citizens in Lin'an

71
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:26,490
who've lived in abject misery.

72
00:08:26,490 --> 00:08:32,549
I just don't want to see the people of the six provinces near Qingyun suffer like them.

73
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:41,870
Right Chancellor Qin.

74
00:08:42,470 --> 00:08:45,188
How is it going? Has he said anything?

75
00:08:46,070 --> 00:08:48,590
Not a word.

76
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:50,470
Fine.

77
00:08:50,470 --> 00:08:54,550
Looks like Fang Tian Lei is determined to keep his mouth shut.

78
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,330
Right Chancellor Qin,

79
00:08:57,090 --> 00:09:01,210
maybe I can open his mouth.

80
00:09:02,629 --> 00:09:04,410
But

81
00:09:07,729 --> 00:09:10,230
you need to promise me one thing.

82
00:09:40,070 --> 00:09:41,670
Open the door!

83
00:09:46,170 --> 00:09:47,929
How is it? Any news about the Holy Master?

84
00:09:47,929 --> 00:09:50,268
He is being kept in the jail of the Secret Investigation Department in the south of the city!

85
00:09:50,268 --> 00:09:53,688
- How many guards are there?
-There are at least forty of them!

86
00:09:54,449 --> 00:09:56,609
Forty.

87
00:09:56,609 --> 00:09:58,168
We still have a chance.

88
00:09:58,168 --> 00:10:00,669
Without further ado, let's go!

89
00:10:20,610 --> 00:10:22,790
I'm not here to arrest you.

90
00:10:24,909 --> 00:10:27,809
Ning Yi knows how to save Fang Tian Lei's life.

91
00:10:27,809 --> 00:10:31,510
He sent me here to stop you from acting on impulse.

92
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:48,970
[Prison]

93
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:12,600
And now they've asked you to interrogate me.

94
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,480
[Biao]

95
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:22,400
What have you done to Xi Gua?

96
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,500
She's safe now,

97
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:27,400
but she only wants to rescue you.

98
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:31,600
Just now, she gathered the people of Badao Camp

99
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:34,800
and was going to break into the jail.

100
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,300
Silly girl!

101
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:41,700
That would be a suicide mission!

102
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:42,800
Yes.

103
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:46,100
So I came to you now

104
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:48,700
and I hope you can stop her.

105
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:54,000
How can I stop her?

106
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:57,000
I've made a deal with Right Chancellor Qin.

107
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,700
He's agreed to my terms.

108
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:02,900
As long as you tell us who the mastermind was of all this,

109
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:05,400
we'll let you walk out of here.

110
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:08,200
If Xi Gua knows that you are safe,

111
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:11,000
she won't come to seek her doom.

112
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:19,400
How can I know that you are not deceiving me?

113
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:22,000
If I tell you that,

114
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,000
then you can kill two birds with one stone,

115
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:27,700
taking down Xi Gua and Badao Camp altogether!

116
00:12:27,700 --> 00:12:30,600
If I had wanted to capture Xi Gua,

117
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,600
do you think she would've been able to leave Lin'an?

118
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:39,600
Staying in Wudu can be very dangerous to her.

119
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:42,800
She could be killed at any time!

120
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:02,100
Right Chancellor Qin,

121
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,800
I've written the things

122
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:13,600
I've promised to do for you on this paper.

123
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:16,100
As for those you promised me…

124
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:18,400
Ask them to get changed

125
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,800
and leave through the north city gate.

126
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:22,700
I've already told them. The gate guards won't stop them.

127
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:26,400
But he has to leave tonight.

128
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,100
I see.

129
00:13:30,300 --> 00:13:32,400
Thank you, Right Chancellor Qin!

130
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,600
"I'm fine."

131
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:56,800
"All of you from Badao Camp leave quickly and don't take any risks again."

132
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,300
"Your lives shall be saved!"

133
00:13:58,300 --> 00:14:02,400
This is truly the Holy Master's handwriting.

134
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,600
We don't have much time left.

135
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:06,800
Change into normal clothes and leave through the north city gate after curfew.

136
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:09,800
How's the Holy Master now?

137
00:14:09,800 --> 00:14:10,900
Don't worry.

138
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:13,200
Commander Ning has managed to exempt him from the death penalty.

139
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:16,300
He said as long as Fang Tian Lei causes no trouble in the jail,

140
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:18,500
he'll guarantee his safe return.

141
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:22,490
[Biao]

142
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,400
Ning Yi,

143
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,800
where is he?

144
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,800
Is he afraid of coming?

145
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:45,000
[Prosperous view]

146
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,600
Open the gate.

147
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:26,100
[North City Gate]

148
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,600
Let's go.

149
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,300
Wait for me here!

150
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,600
Ning Yi.

151
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,800
Show your face!

152
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:29,700
I know you are here!

