♫ Dare not expect depending on your lips and teeth ♫

189
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:27,400
♫ I can only hide my inner affection ♫

190
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:31,200
♫ Even if the tears fall into rain, even if words are like ice ♫

191
