[Pavilion]

200
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:46,800
[Danfeng Gate]

201
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:50,800
Your Majesty, Fang Tian Lei has confessed.

202
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:06,800
Your Majesty, no matter who he mentioned,

203
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:10,300
his sin is not to be tolerated!

204
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:14,400
Your Majesty, please behead him in public right away

205
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:16,700
to comfort all the people!

206
00:22:16,700 --> 00:22:18,200
I agree!

207
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:20,200
Fang Tian Lei has committed the worst crime,

208
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:24,000
yet whoever is behind this defies description!

209
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:32,510
Summon Minister He!

210
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,600
Baili Hongji?

211
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:39,800
Isn't that the Emperor of Jing State?

212
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:42,200
Jing is behind all of this!

213
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,900
Your Majesty! An urgent report from the front line!

214
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,700
Read it!

215
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,800
"Baili Hongji, Emperor of Jing State,

216
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:52,600
sent out a grand army to strike a sudden attack!

217
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:55,300
Our troops were put to a route in the battle in Heshui.

218
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:58,000
100,000 picked soldiers and the Elite Squad of the Secret Investigation Department

219
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,000
were completely annihilated!

220
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:03,600
This morning, the enemy vanguard occupied Xinggu Pass.

221
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:06,200
General Wang Bing and General Yang Shi Ke…

222
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:09,400
What?

223
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:12,800
surrendered after being captured alive.

224
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:30,300
Your Majesty, Right Chancellor Qin is here.

225
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:35,000
- Greetings...
- Right Chancellor Qin, I'm tired now.

226
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:38,800
I've decided to

227
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:42,000
make peace with Jing State.

228
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:44,400
Please go back.

229
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:49,400
I have a bold suggestion.

230
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:52,500
The North Expedition is a national plan.

231
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:56,200
General Dong will soon lead the army to the north with the firearms

232
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:58,900
to take back the six provinces near Qingyun.

233
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:02,300
Your Majesty, I must ask you to think again!

234
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:13,600
Taking back lost territory is never easy.

235
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:19,500
I don't want to see the people and the soldiers suffer any longer!

236
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:25,200
Your Majesty, please think again!

237
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:27,600
Are you pushing me?

238
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,400
I dare not!

239
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:37,300
But if we miss this chance to head north,

240
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:38,500
we'll lose our hope forever!

241
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:42,000
Your Majesty, please think again!

242
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:47,800
Kneel as long as you want!

243
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,000
Come on!

244
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:51,300
Escort me back to Yangshou Hall!

245
00:25:17,100 --> 00:25:17,800
Your Majesty!

246
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:19,200
Get out!

247
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:23,800
Your Majesty, Minster He wants to see you.

248
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:28,200
Let him in!

249
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,400
Yes.

250
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,400
Your Majesty!

251
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:41,200
Minster He, as you were!

252
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:44,400
Thank you, Your Majesty!

253
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:47,310
According to your decree,

254
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:49,400
I've contacted the envoy of Jing State

255
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:51,900
and know their terms for peacemaking.

256
00:25:52,600 --> 00:25:54,200
As long as we agree,

257
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:57,700
they'll withdraw their troops in Xinggu Pass right away.

258
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:59,400
Your Majesty, please review it!

259
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,600
No need.

260
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:01,900
I agree!

261
00:26:01,900 --> 00:26:04,000
Minster He, set out right away!

262
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,600
Thank you for your hard work!

263
00:26:05,600 --> 00:26:07,600
Yes, Your Majesty!

264
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:12,600
Bu to make peace with Jing,

265
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:15,600
they have one more requirement.

266
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:17,200
What is it?

267
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:20,400
Jing State demands Right Chancellor Qin go with me

268
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:25,300
and keep him as a hostage in Jing forever!

269
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:49,200
Right Chancellor Qin.

270
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:58,100
Your Majesty, I didn't expect you'd visit at this hour!

271
00:26:58,100 --> 00:27:00,400
Right Chancellor Qin, please rise!

272
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:06,000
I was quite short-tempered this noon.

273
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,600
I hope you don't mind.

274
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:09,500
I dare not!

275
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:13,900
I don't like wars.

276
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:18,200
If we can make peace with Jing State,

277
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:20,800
then there will be no need to start a war.

278
00:27:23,600 --> 00:27:25,400
I know that you are

279
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:28,400
entrusted with the late Emperor's testamentary edict

280
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:30,100
of taking back the lost territory.

281
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:32,600
But we're living in a different world today.

282
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:36,700
So, I'm here to ask if you can

283
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:39,200
give up on the stubborn loyalty

284
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:43,000
and do me a favor.

285
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:48,400
Your Majesty, may I know what I can do for you?

286
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:57,400
Your Majesty, do you want me to go to Jing State

287
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:02,000
in exchange for the peace of Wu Dynasty?

288
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:05,000
That's the general idea!

289
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:09,400
Right Chancellor Qin, what do you think?

290
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:17,500
Your Majesty, since you've made up your mind,

291
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:23,800
I'm willing to help you make it happen.

292
00:28:37,900 --> 00:28:39,600
Get the sedan ready.

293
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:41,700
Let's go back.

294
00:28:44,330 --> 00:28:48,500
[Qin Manor]

295
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:05,200
Teacher, why do you summon me this late?

296
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:08,800
This will be left to you now.

297
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:10,800
The late Emperor's testamentary edict?

298
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:14,800
Do not let anybody else know about this!

299
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:16,800
I have to go on a long trip.

300
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:20,600
Once General Dong is back, you must give this secret edict

301
00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:23,200
to him in person!

302
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:25,300
General Dong will be back in Wudu in less than three days.

303
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:27,400
- Why don't you…
- I can't wait any longer.

304
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:29,800
You can give it to him.

305
00:29:29,800 --> 00:29:34,000
He should know what to do with it.

306
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:41,400
Understood!

307
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:50,400
[Wudu]

308
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:53,800
[Two days later]

309
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:03,220
[Wu]

310
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,200
Your Highness, I heard

311
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:19,400
that you were detained at the Ministry of Penalty.

312
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:21,600
Why did you come here?

313
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:24,400
Before Right Chancellor Qin left,

314
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:28,200
he freed me from prison.

315
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:32,400
So, where is Right Chancellor Qin?

316
00:30:38,700 --> 00:30:41,800
Your Majesty, please take back your edict.

317
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:43,600
Call back the diplomatic convoy,

318
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:46,400
and send our army to go on an expedition to Jing State!

319
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:51,400
I'm willing to go through fire and water for our country!

320
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,700
General Dong, please don't make any noise!

321
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:55,700
His Majesty is sleeping right now!

322
00:30:55,700 --> 00:30:59,700
You will wake him up and you'll be punished for that!

323
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:03,500
Right Chancellor Qin is even willing to be a hostage for Wu Dynasty!

324
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:05,200
My life is worthless

325
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,900
and means nothing compared to his!

326
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:10,000
If His Majesty refuses to see me,

327
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:15,800
I'll stay here and beg His Majesty until he agrees to see me!

328
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:19,700
Your Majesty, please take back your edict.

329
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:21,200
Call back the diplomatic convoy,

330
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:23,400
and send our army to go on an expedition to Jing State!

331
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:27,600
I'm willing to go through fire and water for our country!

332
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:29,600
Right Chancellor Li, please ask him to stop.

333
00:31:29,600 --> 00:31:33,400
Your Majesty, please take back your edict.

334
