337
00:31:42,300 --> 00:31:49,900
[Border of Jin State]

338
00:31:51,020 --> 00:31:52,590
[Wu]

339
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:08,600
Right Chancellor Qin,

340
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:13,400
even to this day, you can still remain calm.

341
00:32:14,800 --> 00:32:18,600
There's really nothing that makes you reluctant to leave this world

342
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:23,800
or are you just pretending?

343
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:28,800
Minister, why do you say that?

344
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:31,600
And why should I pretend?

345
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:33,800
When you arrive in Jing State,

346
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:36,000
you don't know what will happen.

347
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:41,400
Only God knows if you can survive.

348
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:43,800
Aren't you afraid of death?

349
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:47,200
Of course I am.

350
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,900
If you are,

351
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:53,200
why did you come back from Jiangning

352
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:56,300
instead of living in retirement there?

353
00:32:56,900 --> 00:32:59,500
Speaking of Jiangning,

354
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:05,800
it is quite a nice place to spend your retirement.

355
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:11,200
But it is not too late to enjoy it

356
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:14,800
after the six provinces near Qingyun

357
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:17,200
are taken back.

358
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:24,400
Right Chancellor Qin, you are so concerned about our nation!

359
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,300
I understand.

360
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:28,500
Staying in a peaceful city far away

361
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:32,900
can be torturous to a person like you.

362
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:38,200
However, nothing changes even if you come back.

363
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:41,800
The peacemaking has been decided.

364
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:43,200
Before long,

365
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:48,600
you'll become a disposable and worthless prisoner.

366
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:53,800
The six provinces near Qingyun will never be taken back.

367
00:33:56,200 --> 00:34:01,000
Minister, if that's what you think.

368
00:34:10,100 --> 00:34:14,000
[Yangxin Pavilion]

369
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,000
Report!

370
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,400
Chancellor Li, General Dong!

371
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,800
The cavalry marched all night nonstop

372
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:20,800
trying to catch up with the diplomatic convoy.

373
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:23,400
But the convoy had already passed the northern border and entered the territory of Jing.

374
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:26,200
They were not able to get them back. Please give an order!

375
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,500
General Dong.

376
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,600
This is…

377
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:37,800
Before Right Chancellor Qin left,

378
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:40,200
he asked me to give this to you.

379
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,580
When the late Emperor passed away,

380
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:53,400
he actually passed two edicts.

381
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:57,000
One is to order the Secret Investigation Department to develop firearms in Lin'an

382
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,800
and take back the six provinces near Qingyun,

383
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:04,000
and the other is the one you're seeing right now.

384
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:09,900
Did Right Chancellor Qin say anything else before he left?

385
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,600
Right Chancellor Qin said

386
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:17,500
there is nothing on his mind now

387
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:21,000
and no need to worry about his safety.

388
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,800
Just follow the edict.

389
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,600
Chancellor Li,

390
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:33,400
