391
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:36,000
it'll rust sooner or later!

392
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,900
- Wang Yan!
- Yes!

393
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:40,000
Assemble the three armies!

394
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,700
Head north with me!

395
00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:43,200
Yes!

396
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:52,500
Come on!

397
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:55,900
